@startuml
title Athena JS command docs after CLI-reference pass

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam Rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #D9EAD3
  BorderColor #38761D
}
skinparam ArrowColor #355C7D

actor "Developer" as Dev

rectangle "docs/cli-command-reference.md\n(commands + help + troubleshooting)" as CliRef #D9EAD3
rectangle "docs/index.md\nreading order includes CLI reference" as DocsIndex #CFE2F3
rectangle "README + getting-started + generator-config\nlinked to CLI reference" as LinkedDocs #E2F0D9
rectangle "Standalone guidance\nAthena JS + Athena RS positioning" as Positioning #D0E0E3

Dev --> DocsIndex : start docs flow
DocsIndex --> CliRef : command source of truth
CliRef --> LinkedDocs : shared references
CliRef --> Positioning : runtime split guidance

note right of CliRef
One canonical page now documents:
- all supported commands
- help behavior
- Windows shim recovery
- common error meanings (ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND, 3D000)
end note

@enduml
